sequenceDiagram
    participant External as External Sender
    participant API as Web API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as Message Broker
    participant Worker as Background Worker
    participant Dest as Subscriber App
    External->>API: POST /webhook/{source_id} (Payload)
    activate API
    API->>DB: Insert Job (status: PENDING)
    API->>Queue: Enqueue Job Task
    API-->>External: 202 Accepted (Immediately)
    deactivate API
    Note over Queue, Worker: -- Asynchronous Boundary --
    Worker->>Queue: Poll for Tasks
    activate Worker
    Queue-->>Worker: Return Job Task
    Worker->>DB: Update Job (status: PROCESSING)
    
    Note right of Worker: Executes the "Action" <br>(e.g., transforms Payload)
    
    Worker->>DB: Save Processed Payload
    
    loop For each Subscriber
        Worker->>Dest: POST Processed Payload
        alt Delivery Success
            Dest-->>Worker: 200 OK
            Worker->>DB: Insert DeliveryAttempt (SUCCESS)
        else Delivery Failure (e.g. 500 Error / Timeout)
            Dest-->>Worker: 500 Internal Error
            Worker->>DB: Insert DeliveryAttempt (FAILED)
            Worker->>Queue: Schedule Retry (Exponential Backoff)
        end
    end
    Worker->>DB: Update Job (status: COMPLETED or FAILED)
    deactivate Worker